    "title": "1、数据来源",
    "page_range": "103",
    "summary": "This section outlines the data sourcing methodology for a global mobile game advertising market analysis. It supports retrieval for the following:\n- **Topics:** Global mobile game advertising data, ad intelligence analysis, industry trend tracking.\n- **Entities:** Guangda Big Data Team (data provider), global ad intelligence analysis tool (platform).\n- **Procedures:** Global sampling for ad data collection; hourly data refresh cycles.\n- **Metrics:** Coverage of >70 countries/regions and 80+ ad channels; >1.6 billion accumulated ad records; >1 million records updated daily on an hourly basis.\n- **Claims:** The dataset's scale and update frequency enable reliable identification of macro trends in the advertising industry.\n- **Evidence Types:** Quantitative scale metrics and methodological descriptions (sampling, update frequency).\n- **Not Present:** Specific dates, formal definitions, tables, or figures."
